title: Ahjo makes decision-making transparent and enables electronic archiving (City of Helsinki)
text: ( Source : City of Helsinki ) 26.10. 2015 06:43 The decision-making documents of all City of Helsinki administrative bodies, departments and public enterprises have been processed with the Ahjo information management system since summer 2011 .
